## Create Custom Field Option

```http
POST https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/custom-fields HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Token token=abc123abc123
X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>

{
  "data": {
    "type": "custom-field-options",
    "attributes": {
      "value": "Option value"
    },
		"relationships": {
      "custom-field": {
        "data": {
          "id": 1,
          "type": "custom-fields"
        }
      }
		}
  }
}
```

```shell
curl -X "POST" "https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/custom-fields" \
     -H "Authorization: Token token=abc123abc123" \
     -H "X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>"
     -H "Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json" \
     -d '{
       {
         "data": {
           "type": "custom-field-options",
           "attributes": {
             "value": "Option value"
           },
       		"relationships": {
             "custom-field": {
               "data": {
                 "id": 1,
                 "type": "custom-fields"
               }
             }
       		}
         }
       }
}'
```

> Example response

```json
{
  "data": {
    "id": "1",
    "type": "custom-field-options",
    "links": {
      "self": "https://api.teamtailor.localhost/v1/custom-field-options/1"
    },
    "attributes": {
      "value": "Option value"
    },
    "relationships": {
      "custom-field": {
        "links": {
          "self": "https://api.teamtailor.localhost/v1/custom-field-options/1/relationships/custom-field",
          "related": "https://api.teamtailor.localhost/v1/custom-field-options/1/custom-field"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Create a new custom field option.

<aside class="notice">
  <code>value</code> and <code>relationships</code> are required to be able to save a new custom field option.
</aside>
